      • NurCmdGen2V2

        public NurCmdGen2V2(int password,
                    NurUntraceableParam utrParam)
             throws NurApiException
        Untraceable command without selection parameters.
        Parameters:
        password - Untraceable is always secured; password needs to match.
        utrParam - The unUntraceable command's setup, see NurUntraceableParam.
        Throws:
        NurApiException - Exception can be thrown with parameter, such as bit length, error.
